- reduce the context menu (right mouse) to "set return value"
- make the morph motor time and glide motor time to settings parameters and no more as project parameter
- update return values on load another program
- plugin fix: playback works also if the daw not runs
- disable double click to program value

- rename a lot of buttons
- changed: buttons ALWAYS turn functions on if enabled and off if diabled (some buttons was turning functions off if enabled before))
- fix/change button animations

- change CAPTIONS
-------------------------
- OSC:
----------------
- "MOD OFF" to "O-MOD" (it's now a button to turn the function on) (please invert it in your projects)
- "WAVE" to "WAV-1", "WAV-2"... 
- "OSC 1" to "TUNE-1", "TUNE-2"... 
- "LFO 1"; "LFO 2" to "L-MOD"... 

- FM
----------------
- "OSC PULSE" to "O-PULSE"
- "OSC SWITCH" to "O-SWCH"

- general
- "MOD (%)" to "MOD %" (shorter, more readable)

- add shortcuts to the area captions. EXAMPLE: "OSCILLATORS" to "OSCILLATORS (O)"

